      "id": "PopularPost356398",
      "post_content": "I'm surprised no one has mentioned that this, but you can actually use the ability while blocking as well, making it a 3/5 blocker and potentially killing something. If you're interested in 0/6 artifact blockers, by the way, here's a short list:  \n  \n- [Living Wall](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Living Wall) - Regenerates  \n- [Shield Sphere](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Shield Sphere) - Free! And shrinks after repeated assaults  \n- [Mobile Fort](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mobile Fort) - Functionally identical  \n- [Junktroller](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Junktroller) - Card Recycling  \n- [Wall of Tanglecord](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wall of Tanglecord) - Activated reach  \n- [Guardians of Meletis](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Guardians of Meletis) - Nice flavor text  ",
      "posted_by": "Equinox523",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost356398\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">I'm surprised no one has mentioned that this, but you can actually use the ability while blocking as well, making it a 3/5 blocker and potentially killing something.  If you're interested in 0/6 artifact blockers, by the way, here's a short list:<br/><br/>- <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Living Wall\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Living Wall\">Living Wall</a> - Regenerates<br/>- <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Shield Sphere\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Shield Sphere\">Shield Sphere</a> - Free! And shrinks after repeated assaults<br/>- <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mobile Fort\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mobile Fort\">Mobile Fort</a> - Functionally identical<br/>- <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Junktroller\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Junktroller\">Junktroller</a> - Card Recycling<br/>- <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Wall of Tanglecord\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wall of Tanglecord\">Wall of Tanglecord</a> - Activated reach<br/>- <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Guardians of Meletis\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Guardians of Meletis\">Guardians of Meletis</a> - Nice flavor text<br/></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '356398'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<di